name: The Lighthouse #1
description:
First image of the "Lighthouse Collection". The entire "Lighthouse Collection" use the same photograph as a base, which can be found on mi ig and soon as nft in H=N. All the images of the collection are generated by CLIP guided diffusion and edited in photoshop.

The "Lighthouse Collection" is intended to be the first collection of a project that explores the ai generated art mixed with photos.
